<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Saqib Ali | Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #08111f;
      --panel: rgba(9, 23, 41, 0.82);
      --panel-strong: rgba(4, 12, 24, 0.92);
      --text: #f3fbff;
      --muted: #9fb7c9;
      --line: rgba(90, 219, 255, 0.18);
      --accent: #5ad2ff;
      --accent-2: #8effc1;
      --shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      --radius: 24px;
      --container: 1120px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(142, 255, 193, 0.12), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #020712 0%, #071326 50%, #020712 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(calc(100% - 2rem), var(--container));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(2, 9, 20, 0.76);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .navbar {
      min-height: 76px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .nav-links {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 96px 0 72px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow,
    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lead,
    .section-text,
    .card p,
    .project-card p,
    .contact-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 155px;
      padding: 0.95rem 1.35rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #baf6ff);
      color: #03111f;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.25);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border-color: var(--line);
      background: rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.07);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .hero-card,
    .card,
    .project-card,
    .contact-card,
    .skill-box {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), var(--panel-strong));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .status {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(142, 255, 193, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(142, 255, 193, 0.2);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(142, 255, 193, 0.7);
    }

    .profile-wrap {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.4), rgba(142, 255, 193, 0.12));
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .profile-wrap img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .mini-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .mini-card {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .mini-card span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: 32px 0 88px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .section-heading h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .about-grid,
    .skills-grid,
    .project-grid,
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    }

    .card,
    .project-card,
    .contact-card,
    .skill-box {
      padding: 1.35rem;
    }

    .card h3,
    .project-card h3,
    .contact-card h3,
    .skill-box h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
    }

    .skill-list,
    .project-tags,
    .contact-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .skill-list span,
    .project-tags span,
    .contact-list span {
      padding: 0.52rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.16);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .project-no {
      color: rgba(90, 210, 255, 0.4);
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .contact-card a.inline-link {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 22px 0 34px;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .about-grid,
      .skills-grid,
      .project-grid,
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .navbar,
      .hero-actions,
      .nav-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .nav-links {
        gap: 0.7rem;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 72px;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container navbar">
      <a href="#home" class="brand">SAQIB ALI</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
        <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">BSCS Student | Kasur, Pakistan</p>
          <h1>Saqib Ali</h1>
          <h2>Web Developer, AI Learner, WordPress Designer</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            I build clean, modern, and practical digital experiences with a strong interest in web development,
            SEO, WordPress, and beginner-level AI engineering.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Me</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="status">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            Available for freelance work
          </div>
          <div class="profile-wrap">
            <img src="saqib-portfolio/image/profile.jpeg" alt="Saqib Ali profile photo">
          </div>
          <div class="mini-grid">
            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Core Focus</span>
              Web Development + AI Learning
            </div>
            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Specialty</span>
              WordPress Design and SEO
            </div>
            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Approach</span>
              Fast, polished, and practical solutions
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-kicker">About Me</p>
          <h2>Turning ideas into useful and modern web experiences.</h2>
          <p class="section-text">
            I am Saqib Ali, a passionate BSCS student from Kasur, Pakistan. I enjoy building websites, exploring
            artificial intelligence, designing in WordPress and Canva, and improving online visibility through SEO.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Web Development</h3>
            <p>Responsive websites using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, Bootstrap, and SQL-based workflows.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>AI Exploration</h3>
            <p>Learning machine learning, model training, and data science fundamentals through hands-on practice.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>SEO and Design</h3>
            <p>Creating better structure, stronger visibility, and cleaner presentation for digital products.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-kicker">Skills</p>
          <h2>Technical strengths across coding, design, and productivity.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <article class="skill-box">
            <h3>Languages and Web</h3>
            <div class="skill-list">
              <span>Python</span>
              <span>PHP</span>
              <span>HTML</span>
              <span>CSS</span>
              <span>JavaScript</span>
              <span>Bootstrap</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="skill-box">
            <h3>Database and Tools</h3>
            <div class="skill-list">
              <span>SQL</span>
              <span>XAMPP</span>
              <span>VS Code</span>
              <span>Jupyter</span>
              <span>Google Colab</span>
              <span>Kaggle</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="skill-box">
            <h3>AI and Data</h3>
            <div class="skill-list">
              <span>Machine Learning</span>
              <span>Deep Learning</span>
              <span>Model Training</span>
              <span>Data Science Basics</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="skill-box">
            <h3>Design and Office</h3>
            <div class="skill-list">
              <span>WordPress</span>
              <span>Canva</span>
              <span>SEO</span>
              <span>MS Word</span>
              <span>Excel</span>
              <span>PowerPoint</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-kicker">Projects</p>
          <h2>Selected work that blends interface design, logic, and data thinking.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="project-grid">
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-no">01</div>
            <h3>AgroCare Website</h3>
            <p>A modern agriculture website built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, PHP, and SQL.</p>
            <div class="project-tags">
              <span>HTML</span>
              <span>CSS</span>
              <span>JavaScript</span>
              <span>PHP</span>
              <span>SQL</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-no">02</div>
            <h3>Online Tour Booking System</h3>
            <p>A booking platform for tours with front-end pages, backend logic, and reservation workflow.</p>
            <div class="project-tags">
              <span>Booking</span>
              <span>Bootstrap</span>
              <span>PHP</span>
              <span>SQL</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-no">03</div>
            <h3>Student Management Data Analysis</h3>
            <p>A Python-based data project for analyzing student records and extracting trends and insights.</p>
            <div class="project-tags">
              <span>Python</span>
              <span>Jupyter</span>
              <span>Colab</span>
              <span>Kaggle</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-kicker">Contact</p>
          <h2>Let's connect and build something meaningful together.</h2>
          <p class="section-text">For freelance work, collaboration, or project discussion, you can reach me here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-grid">
          <article class="contact-card">
            <h3>Contact Details</h3>
            <p>Feel free to message me through WhatsApp, GitHub, or LinkedIn.</p>
            <div class="contact-list">
              <span>Kasur, Pakistan</span>
              <span>BSCS Student</span>
              <span>0329 3344426</span>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="contact-card">
            <h3>Online Profiles</h3>
            <p><a class="inline-link" href="https://github.com/saqib-stack-hub">GitHub</a></p>
            <p><a class="inline-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/saqib-ali-135238366">LinkedIn</a></p>
            <p><a class="inline-link" href="https://wa.me/923293344426">WhatsApp</a></p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 Saqib Ali. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
